title: The International Bad Boys Hour Ep 59: Chelsea's Back From The Darkness
description: Chelsea is fresh out of the County Hospital and back in the studio ready to rock!  Steve listens as Chelsea let's everyone in how crazy her last month has been. There is a fine line between brilliant and crazy!
